title: Moist pumpkin traybake
ingredients: ['4 eggs', '250ml vegetable oil', '400g caster sugar', '425g pumpkin puree', '250g plain flour', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '2 teaspoons ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '1/2 teaspoon ground cloves', '1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg']
